{"pr_number": 8440, "pr_title": "ISPN-11782 xsite monitoring and troubleshooting", "pr_createdAt": "2020-06-08T09:58:11Z", "pr_url": "https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan/pull/8440", "timeline": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQzNjU4NTI5Mg==", "url": "https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan/pull/8440#discussion_r436585292", "bodyText": "@pruivo hey I think there are other trace messages that we might want to add here. For example \"IRAC operation failed!\" but I couldn't find any identifier (ISPN0000) and I'm not quite sure about them. Do you think we should add those messages here?", "author": "oraNod", "createdAt": "2020-06-08T10:01:00Z", "path": "documentation/src/main/asciidoc/topics/ref_logs_xsite.adoc", "diffHunk": "@@ -0,0 +1,65 @@\n+[id='xsite_logs-{context}']\n+= Cross-Site Log Messages\n+{brandname} prints different log messages related to cross-site replication.", "originalCommit": "64581c8910e44d3a2acfe1561123acb42878b1a7", "replyToReviewId": null, "replies": null, "type": "inlineReview"}, {"oid": "1bea25d2d485937fc13aa4655b36d1d5372bda95", "url": "https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan/commit/1bea25d2d485937fc13aa4655b36d1d5372bda95", "message": "ISPN-11782 xsite monitoring and troubleshooting", "committedDate": "2020-06-19T14:04:28Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid": "47a40a260b6908e114737b478e1e5c9bb5b53eb2", "url": "https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan/commit/47a40a260b6908e114737b478e1e5c9bb5b53eb2", "message": "ISPN-11782 xsite monitoring and troubleshooting", "committedDate": "2020-06-19T15:29:01Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid": "56bc6452b3f4758c8c32ecd564da1f251b05e9ad", "url": "https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan/commit/56bc6452b3f4758c8c32ecd564da1f251b05e9ad", "message": "ISPN-11782 xsite monitoring and troubleshooting", "committedDate": "2020-06-23T09:34:23Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ0NDI1NDkyMw==", "url": "https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan/pull/8440#discussion_r444254923", "bodyText": "we don't allow TRACE in runtime (without restarting the server). You can enable DEBUG.", "author": "pruivo", "createdAt": "2020-06-23T14:11:27Z", "path": "documentation/src/main/asciidoc/topics/proc_troubleshooting_xsite.adoc", "diffHunk": "@@ -0,0 +1,53 @@\n+[id='xsite_tshoot-{context}']\n+= Collecting Logs and Troubleshooting Cross-Site Replication\n+Diagnose and resolve issues related to {brandname} cross-site replication. Use\n+the {brandname} Command Line Interface (CLI) to adjust log levels at run-time\n+and perform cross-site troubleshooting.\n+\n+.Procedure\n+\n+. Open a terminal in `{server_home}`.\n+. Create a {brandname} CLI connection.\n+. Adjust run-time logging levels to capture DEBUG or TRACE messages if necessary.\n++\n+For example, the following command enables TRACE log messages for the org.infinispan.XSITE category:\n++\n+[source,options=\"nowrap\",subs=attributes+]\n+----\n+[//containers/default]> logging set --level=TRACE org.infinispan.XSITE", "originalCommit": "56bc6452b3f4758c8c32ecd564da1f251b05e9ad", "replyToReviewId": null, "replies": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ0NDMwOTIyMw==", "url": "https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan/pull/8440#discussion_r444309223", "bodyText": "updated", "author": "oraNod", "createdAt": "2020-06-23T15:22:56Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ0NDI1NDkyMw=="}], "type": "inlineReview"}, {"oid": "5ad3a436940bd23a56834449ff7b4ad1a18aed93", "url": "https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan/commit/5ad3a436940bd23a56834449ff7b4ad1a18aed93", "message": "ISPN-11782 xsite monitoring and troubleshooting", "committedDate": "2020-06-23T15:22:20Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid": "601521a8367f284097618c1f1fcf6153a62b73a8", "url": "https://github.com/infinispan/infinispan/commit/601521a8367f284097618c1f1fcf6153a62b73a8", "message": "ISPN-11782 xsite monitoring and troubleshooting", "committedDate": "2020-06-24T08:26:50Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid":